    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们都无法避免老去的那天，你有想过那时的生活会有哪些变化吗？有想过老后的自己是什么样的吗？老病是生死之间的必要演习，也是完整人生的必要组成部分。 在这款游戏中，你将扮演一个管理者，来到一个全是老人的小镇，在这里你将接触到形形色色的老人，和爷爷奶奶们建立情感联系，感受他们的日常生活，体味百态人生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/d784f03863e59bdeabded9a842936fc6.poster.avif?t=1740116183\" width=596 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/d784f03863e59bdeabded9a842936fc6.webm?t=1740116183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/d784f03863e59bdeabded9a842936fc6.mp4?t=1740116183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>---------------丰富的居民生态---------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >七大区域百位居民，他们都有着自己的社交娱乐倾向，也会生病会离世。每个人都是独特而鲜活的个体，他们都是身边随处可见，平凡但又有着独特个性的老人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/33bfebfa18da8ca79f2df84bc4d3d8fd.poster.avif?t=1740116183\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/33bfebfa18da8ca79f2df84bc4d3d8fd.webm?t=1740116183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/33bfebfa18da8ca79f2df84bc4d3d8fd.mp4?t=1740116183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>---------------轻松休闲的玩法---------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >负责小镇的建设满足老人们的各种需求，聘请护工看护身体恶化的居民，为临终的居民确定医疗计划……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/0ca7a983a90cf4e7f96f82a3f18bc410.poster.avif?t=1740116183\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/0ca7a983a90cf4e7f96f82a3f18bc410.webm?t=1740116183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/0ca7a983a90cf4e7f96f82a3f18bc410.mp4?t=1740116183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>---------------趣味的科普元素------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >团队一脉相承的科普要素，玩的过程中了解到有趣的养老小知识。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >养老社区，老后破产，认知症……这些东西离我们很远，也离我们很近。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/1652db7fafb68616339878bfbe70244f.poster.avif?t=1740116183\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/1652db7fafb68616339878bfbe70244f.webm?t=1740116183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/1652db7fafb68616339878bfbe70244f.mp4?t=1740116183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>---------------精致的手绘画风----------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色和场景上做了精心的风格化设计，多采用温暖的色调打造的美丽温馨的老人之城。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/1e258ed9483acb9f34c79fd316f5f57f.poster.avif?t=1740116183\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/1e258ed9483acb9f34c79fd316f5f57f.webm?t=1740116183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/1e258ed9483acb9f34c79fd316f5f57f.mp4?t=1740116183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/035c12fdedc0ae0397d1243ecd88321a.poster.avif?t=1740116183\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/035c12fdedc0ae0397d1243ecd88321a.webm?t=1740116183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/035c12fdedc0ae0397d1243ecd88321a.mp4?t=1740116183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/11819c7ad073a4a40e0fd4f68a247105.poster.avif?t=1740116183\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/11819c7ad073a4a40e0fd4f68a247105.webm?t=1740116183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/11819c7ad073a4a40e0fd4f68a247105.mp4?t=1740116183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/f57508031fdfc1ecefbaccef28ee2aea.poster.avif?t=1740116183\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/f57508031fdfc1ecefbaccef28ee2aea.webm?t=1740116183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264000/extras/f57508031fdfc1ecefbaccef28ee2aea.mp4?t=1740116183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
